column2: select   P.ra as sdss_ra, P.dec as sdss_dec, W.ra as wise_ra, W.dec as wise_dec,  P.psfmag_r as psfMag_r, W.w1mpro as w1mpro, P.cModelMag_u, p.cModelMagErr_u, p.cModelMag_g, p.cModelMagErr_g, p.cModelMag_r, p.cModelMagErr_r, p.cModelMag_i, p.cModelMagErr_i, p.cModelMag_z, p.cModelMagErr_z, p.modelMag_u, p.modelMagErr_u, p.modelMag_g, p.modelMagErr_g, p.modelMag_r, p.modelMagErr_r, p.modelMag_i, p.modelMagErr_i, p.modelMag_z, p.modelMagErr_z,p.petroMag_u, p.petroMag_r, p.petroR5#_r, p.petroR9#_r, p.expRad_u, p.expRad_g, p.expRad_r, p.expRad_i, p.expAB_u, p.expAB_g, p.expAB_r, p.expAB_i, p.fracDeV_u, p.fracDeV_g, p.fracDeV_r, p.fracDeV_i, p.extinction_u, p.extinction_g, p.extinction_r, p.extinction_i, S.z as redshift from wise_xmatch as X   join wise_allsky as W on X.wise_cntr = W.cntr  join photoTag as P on X.sdss_objid = P.objid  join SpecObj as S on X.sdss_objid = S.bestobjid where P.nchild = # and P.dec between # and # and S.z between # and #
